**Story**

Once upon a time in the jungle, there lived a lion and a mouse.
One fine day, while the lion was sleeping, he got disturbed by a mouse who jumped upon him accidently
Lion got angry and caught the mouse in his paws. The cute mouse was in deep despair and started requesting to let him go.
The kind- hearted lion left him and allowed him to go. 

The next day the lion was caught by a hunter in his net. He roared and shouted for help. Suddenly the mouse heard him.
He came for help. The mouse started to eat the net with his sharp teeth to tear it off and help the lion. He succeeeded in that.
The mouse and the lion stayed happily ever after that. 